name: Begin Landing Your Troops & The Dark Path
Text: 'Deploy on table. Your [Seperatists icon] droids are power +1 and may shuttle from battleground systems for free. During battle may place this effect out of play to cancel and redraw your just-drawn destiny. Once per turn, each player may ignore any deployment cost on [Virtual Block 4] Watch Your Step and once per game, while that Objective on table, you may take a starfighter into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle (or draw two cards from your Reserve Deck). Jedi Tests may not modify your battle or weapon destiny draws. Lost if your [Virtual Block 4] objective on table. (Immune to Alter.)',
